#: contents/ui/Import.qml:13
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:window"
msgid "Import Sudoku"
msgstr "匯入數獨"

#: contents/ui/Import.qml:35
#, kde-format
msgctxt "Use en dash for number range"
msgid ""
"Enter or paste a string of 81 characters. 1–9 for given cells, 0 or any "
"single non-numeric character except space will do for blanks cells. PuMoKu "
"will check that the Sudoku is solvable and calculate the level.\n"
"\n"
"Line breaks and spaces are silently removed, so that you can enter one row "
"per-line with some optional whitespace."
msgstr ""
"輸入或貼上代表數獨的 81 個字元。1–9 代表指定方格，0 或其他非數字或空格的字元"
"代表空白方格。PuMoKu 會檢查數獨是否可解之後計算關卡。\n"
"\n"
"換行和空格會被忽略，所以您可以一列方格用一行字輸入或是加上空格。"

